<h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 0;">{{subject}}</h2>
<p style="color: #4b5563;">{{content}}</p>
{{#if completionRate}}
<div style="background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #1e40af; font-weight: 600;">프로필 완성도: {{completionRate}}%</p>
  <div style="background-color: #e0e7ff; border-radius: 4px; height: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
    <div style="background-color: #3b82f6; height: 100%; width: {{completionRate}}%; border-radius: 4px;"></div>
  </div>
</div>
{{/if}}
<p style="color: #4b5563;">프로필을 완성하면 맞춤 공고를 추천받을 수 있습니다.</p>
<a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="btn" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #3b82f6; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;">프로필 완성하기</a>
<p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 16px;">본 메일은 잡차자에서 자동 발송되었습니다.</p>
